transcript:
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Hanji. Deepak sir good afternoon.
Customer: Bhai. Raju bol raha tha side India Mart se aapne koi photo share kiya kya hame?
Executive: Are yaar nahi chal raha tha subah se wo upload nahi ho raha tha koi document upload nahi ho raha tha.
Customer: Login kijiye login kijiye fir se login kijiye.
Executive: Yaar do teen dafe login kiya nikala nikala gaya fir uske baad abhi subah 10 baje ka try karta tha abhi aapka system chalu hua aur upload hona chalu hua.
Customer: To abhi theek ho gaya hai?
Executive: 10 minute pehle 10 minute pehle theek hua maine aapka wo kya naam hai usko bhi baat kiya sabne karke dikhaya.
Executive: To aapko maine apna number bataya tha na bata diya tha mujhe call karke.
Customer: Ye Reliance manager hai na Akash Deep Singh.
Executive: Haan. Wo wo line pe aaya tha usko bhi share kiya.
Executive: Dekho maine aapko hi bheja hai ye mera number hai maine to kafi baar aapko call kiya aap mujhe turant bata diya karo na koi bhi issue hota tha main turant photo kara dunga.
Customer: Theek hai. Theek hai theek hai theek hai.
Executive: To abhi login ho gaya theek hai sab?
Customer: Abhi abhi wo abhi do panch minute pehle main khane ja raha tha main bola chalo karke dekhta hu to ho gaya fir.
Executive: Achcha. Theek hai aur.
Customer: To kabhi kabhi matlab technical glitch ho jata hai theek hai but wo turant I think ho jata hai wo.
Executive: Aur maine kya kya kya aa raha tha wo bhi maine whatsapp kiya dekha aapne?
Customer: Haan aapne bheja hai mere paas photo uska main aapko deta hu yahi hai na.
Executive: Something went wrong wali na.
Customer: Haan haan haan haan.
Executive: Ye dekho maine aapko whatsapp pe diya just mere paas abhi maine abhi dekha isko to isliye maine aapko call kiya theek hai to aap mujhe bata sakte ho koi bhi dekho koi bhi dikkat hota tha.
Customer: Theek hai theek hai theek hai.
Executive: Aur koi dikkat baki calls wagairah to improve ho gaya main dekh raha hu theek hai abhi main kuch kar raha hu to ja raha hai mere khyal se hai na.
Executive: Calls badh raha hai. Leads theek hua abhi buyleads?
Customer: Haan abhi theek hai.
Executive: Haan. Theek hua theek hua.
Customer: Aur mujhe Amar ji se baat karni thi sir Amar Patel ji se.
Executive: Haan to lunch ke baad lunch ke baad karate hai baat.
Executive: Theek hai theek hai ek feedback mil jayega please satisfied kar dijiyega theek hai.
Customer: Haan abhi to main bhi lunch mein ja raha hu sir 12 baje lunch ho jata hai.
Executive: Kitne baje call karu?
Customer: Amar ji ko main phone karke batata hu chalo na.
Executive: Haan bata dijiye theek hai aur wo teen din Patan Patan Gujarat mein the Patan shadi mein gaye unke bua ke waha shadi thi wahi gaye.
Executive: Achcha sorry theek hai theek hai theek hai chalo theek hai aap teen din baad matlab wo baat kar payenge na fir to.
Customer: Ji haan haan ji haan ji.
Executive: Theek hai koi nahi unko laga lunga main aap fir bhi bata dijiyega halaki dekh lijiyega ye na main aapko feedback mil jayega theek hai satisfied mark kar dijiyega theek hai.
Customer: Theek hai theek hai theek hai lunch ke baad.
Executive: Theek hai theek hai thank you.
Customer: Okay okay.
